@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = ((0.37 / tmp) - (wp.cos(v0 + 0.76) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.9)))
    v0 = ((0.26 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.91)) * ((v0 + 0.29 / tmp + 0.37) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.95)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.13 + v1 + 0.63)) / wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = v2
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
